platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We were hoping to avoid making baseball puns, but heres the problem: The MLB app really does knock it out of the park. Its a great way to preview the days matchups, buy tickets to a game, and follow along via live pitch tracking and high-resolution ballpark renderings.
